<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Distribution map of P. aurea (Klug), P. binghami Bischoff, P. dhofarensis sp. nov., and P. maura Bischoff in the Arabian Peninsula." , "Figure 33. Male genitalia A, B Pseudophotopsis aurea (Klug), dorsal and ventral views, respectively C, D P. dhofarensis sp. nov., dorsal and ventral views, respectively." , "Figure 11. Pseudophotopsis dhofarensis sp. nov. (Male) A, B habitus, lateral and dorsal views, respectively C head, frontal view D head, antennal scape and pedicel, dorsal view." , "Figure 12. Pseudophotopsis dhofarensis sp. nov. (Male) A head, fronto-lateral view B antenna C mandible, lateral view D mesosoma, dorsal view." , "Figure 14. Pseudophotopsis dhofarensis sp. nov. (Male) A, B metasoma, dorsal and ventral views, respectively C 2 nd and 3 rd metasomal segments, ventro-lateral view D T 6 - T 7, dorsal view." , "Figure 13. Pseudophotopsis dhofarensis sp. nov. (Male) A head and mesosoma, lateral view B right fore wing." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537894" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537895" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537892" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537882" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537893" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537914" .

